&lt;p&gt;Your job is to build what the spec says, flag what the spec missed, and close the gap between design and working software in two-week sprints.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As AI agent-based automation grows alongside our RPA practice, this role requires genuine fluency across both — UiPath for process automation, and Claude-powered agent workflows for AI-driven solutions. The developer who thrives here is comfortable in both worlds and curious about where they intersect.&lt;/p&gt;
